name: BitSwagger (BTCSWAG)
description: This project aims to create a fun & rewarding project for our community of token holders, and holders of our other crypto & digital products, including Bitcoin Runes, Alkanes, and Ordinals! On several EVM blockchains we have nfts, and are verified artists on Rarible! BitSwagger (BTCSWAG) on BASE, was developed with a small supply after 17% burns, 26% locked up until 2028, and as of July 28th, we proudly added staking and actual utility to our token! Our company was filed with the Secretary of State of Ohio, on March 1, 2025! BitSwagger Digital Studios LLC dba BtcSwag, LLC, was filed for further transparency & security, we are an Ohio Company, USA!
